data.description: Don't Pass Me By! Located in the Billings Heights (East Bench).  Single Level with 4 Bedrooms, 1 & 1/2  Bathrooms, Living Room, Kitchen and an attached oversize two car garage! The home is across the street from Hawthorne Park. Also featuring a huge fenced yard that’s great for those backyard bbq’s and entertainment. A large shed that provides storage for yard and garden supplies. This wonderful house features its original hardwood flooring, a wood fireplace and a newer roof. Don’t miss out on this opportunity and schedule a showing today!
